Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.70,0:21:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)}{\pos(355,355)}{\1c&H00d6cb50}欢迎神!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.80,0:21:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的俘虏了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.46,0:23:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么长时间辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的只有这些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.08,0:23:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三九寒天锻炼身心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.40,0:23:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}{\pos(350,320)}{\1c&H0072cfd6}下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.40,0:23:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}{\pos(355,355)}{\1c&H002dcec4}欢迎小岬!
